strings.Value: [Attack] "You little bastard! I'm going to get you!"
"Ah, adventurers! Look at my offers! New wares! In a new bag! All new, all bestest! Only me be old â€” can't be any bester!"
"You know! No? Sellers be where fair be! No one be calling us, we come where the buying is! We be profeshional traders!"

"Ha! Look at his pitiful stuff! No much choice for a Hero to buy, eh?" {n}Nok-Nok eyes the trader's goods with obvious greed, though he still manages to turn around with feigned disdain.{/n}
